data.description: Come home to this well maintained single family home in Lovejoy Crossing! This 2-story house built in 2020 features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and 2 car garage. Downstairs features an open concept design with 9-foot ceilings, open kitchen with large island, pantry, breakfast area and a large family room with an electric fireplace. Upstairs features full hall bathroom with double vanity and 2 guest bedrooms. Upstairs owner suite features trey ceiling, walk-in closet, large bathroom with tub and separate shower, and double vanity. Patio in backyard. Schedule your appointment today. You don’t want to miss this one, it will not last!
